author: lgo
msg: Follow up r26920, fix update_tests.py 38: on Windows, using the apr calls svn
can only execute external applications that are considered executable
(.bat, .exe etc). So when we want svn to call .py scripts we have to use the
same trick as for the hook scripts, ie. add a batch file to wrap the .py file.
(global): on Windows use svneditor.bat as the svneditor_script.
